sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Intel Corp (Symbol: INTC), where a total of 115,869 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 11.6 million underlying shares.
That amounts to about 52% of INTC's average daily trading volume over the past month of 22.3 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $65 strike call option expiring July 02, 2020, with 36,347 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 3.6 million underlying shares of INTC.
